instructions: From any Home screen, tap Apps . Tap Browser . Tap Menu . Tap Settings . Tap Privacy & security . Tap one of the following options: Clear cache Clear all cookie data Clear history Tap OK .
From any webpage, tap the Tabs icon. Tap NEW TAB or NEW INCOGNITO TAB to open, or tap the white X to close.
From any Home screen, tap the Apps icon. Tap Internet . Tap the Menu key. Tap Settings . Tap Advanced . Tap Download storage . Select the storage location: Storage card Phone storage
From any Home screen, tap Apps . Tap Browser . Tap Menu . Tap Settings . Tap Advanced . Select the Enable JavaScript check box to turn it on. Clear the Enable JavaScript check box to turn it off.
